          "message": { "text": "Volunteer entity diverges (additively) across backends: .NET adds InternalIdHash/FirstName/LastName/RoleId; Android VolunteerEntity keys on MappingName only. ACCEPTED BY DESIGN (ADR-016) — Android has no SMS-approval flow and never reads those columns; not migrated (Room @Entity change carries the ADR-004 data-wipe hazard). Codified in a VolunteerEntity.kt header comment + tools/parity.md #3. [ISS-003, accepted]" },
