          "message": { "text": "One REST + domain contract is implemented three times with no shared source of truth (.NET Program.cs, Android Ktor routes, React services; entity model triplicated) and no tests. ACCEPTED BY DESIGN (dual-target architecture, ADR-001/012/015) and now GUARDED by a 0-LLM constant parity lint (tools/parity-lint.mjs, ADR-018) for ReminderTypes/SmsStatuses/DayGroups; the refresh-token TTL 7d/3d and password-policy differences are recorded accepted divergences. Endpoint/DTO shapes are still hand-mirrored. [ISS-004, accepted]" },
